    "Such behavior could limit the GA's ability to identify diverse and potentially more challenging execution paths, ultimately affecting the robustness of the WCET estimation.",
    "Conversely, introducing diversity alongside execution time in the fitness evaluation results in a steadier increase in execution times across generations.",
    "This indicates a more comprehensive exploration of the solution space, as the GA considers a wider array of solution variants.",
    "By integrating diversity, the algorithm avoids premature convergence and encourages varied solution paths, enhancing the thoroughness of the WCET estimation process.",
    "This analysis highlights the importance of diversity in the fitness function of GAs for WCET estimation."
